19 (b) Both parents of a child born in lawful wedlock if living, the
20 surviving parent of a child born in lawful wedlock, the mother of a child
21 born out of wedlock, or both the mother and father of a child born out of
22 wedlock as determined pursuant to sections 43-104.08 to 43-104.24.
23 (2) A written consent or relinquishment for adoption under this
24 section shall not be valid unless signed at least forty-eight hours after
